Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:57.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:03.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:13.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:20.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have as many second \Nhelpings as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us that you can eat as much as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks! It's really really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the Straw Hats are enjoying\Nour homemade dishes so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I don't like the look of those clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're big! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--It punched a hole in the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} and everybody! Get inside now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?! We'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way should we turn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your navigator?! Give us directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we don't have a navigator\Nsince we were a land-based gang originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're in the New World, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Grandma? It's me, Gambia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, huge hail \Njust started falling on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we're in trouble,\Nwe call Grandma in our hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So she knows about the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some chewing gum\Nstuck to the deck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and we didn't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap the hailstone in cloth\Nand cool the gum to peel it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came off surprisingly easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don¬Å't need that sort of wisdom now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! You got hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apply sugar to his lump, she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with her wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! This ship's gonna sink!\NNami, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had so many ships to choose from\Nbut we got on board the wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we gotta deal with this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we had the Sunny's equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you using your barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Well, Grandma says,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You'll regret it if you defy nature!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so scared, get back on land!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice!\NI'll smash all the hailstones up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We have the Straw Hats \Nwho don't even fear god
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's like getting help \Nfrom a thousand people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our appreciation rains down\Nlike hail and snow pellets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you guys survived until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just a short time \Nuntil we arrive at Zou,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I get to travel\Nwith that awesome Luffy-senpai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm too happy and I could be punished for it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do something too, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Silver Fortress!\NLuffy and Barto's Great Adventure!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to pee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I'm so happy to have a pee\Nwith my hero, Luffy-senpai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm hungry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you want me\Nto fix you a midnight snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is it hailing again?\N--I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, neither of us can swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we landed the unwanted one too though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually lured Straw Hat with meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you said, Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pirate Hunter." "God."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cyborg." "Demon Child."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Let's do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as we planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a former leader of the Sweet \NPirates from the East Blue - Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yoroshiku{\i0} (Thanks) !
